column2: SELECT TOP # G.modelFlux_z,  G.modelFluxIvar_u,G.modelFluxIvar_g,G.modelFluxIvar_r,G.modelFluxIvar_i,G.modelFluxIvar_z,GN.distance FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN JOIN Galaxy AS G ON GN.objID = G.objID JOIN PhotoTag AS pt ON pt.objID = G.objID JOIN Photoz AS pz ON GN.objID = pz.objID ORDER by distance
